{"tid":1034834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國國會擬強迫14個海外屬土批准同性婚姻合法化","createTime":"2019-02-24T08:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T08:30:24.000Z","uid":238370,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"39cb3895605a9732ced98f806d1cab91c971103f","tid":1034834,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:09:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1440312/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1440312%2F&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=516eda31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1440312%2F&h=102b2ec8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1440312/</a><br />\n<br />\n英國國會外交事務委員會本周發表一份報告，指英國應該強迫海外屬土批准同性婚姻合法化。一些海外屬土擁有本身的議會、憲法和司法管轄權，在這個議題上持相反立場。<br />\n<br />\n該委員會在一份題為《全球英國及英國海外屬土：重定關係》的報告中，罕有地提出干預14個海外屬土在這個議題上的政策。其中5個屬土－－包括位於加勒比海的安圭拉和英屬處女島，都有法例禁止同性婚姻。<br />\n<br />\n同性婚姻現時在英國本土是合法的，只有北愛爾蘭例外。報告指出：「現在是時候要所有海外屬土都實行同性婚姻合法化。英國政府不單只是原則上支持，而是要作出更大努力，去達到這個目標。」<br />\n<br />\n英國政府2001年已下令所有海外屬土把同性戀非刑事化，但自此之後，英國便沒有採取更多行動為同性戀者及跨性別人士爭取更大權益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大英帝國萬歲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69d3443f759164522027566a69620106c640d23","tid":1034834,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:09:39.000Z","msg":"不合法就獨立"},{"pid":"102f3ed38d479da67ebf94af79369a96f4f06e55","tid":1034834,"uid":18012,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:10:39.000Z","msg":"迫d gay 佬去荒島<br />\n其實幾好"},{"pid":"20a6c82f64ce857d982246ce520a6a6b510f1844","tid":1034834,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"香港就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7854b1636825cc31e1642d6c034741f25c8f13f4","tid":1034834,"uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:13:21.000Z","msg":"議會專政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等同淫大強行實施法律"},{"pid":"cbf9633a6786a0c87fce3c30b047c019e36d109e","tid":1034834,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:16:39.000Z","msg":"英國議制不斷令社會進步<br />\n香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b300ed902beee223ef52d4e465e977e16b0503c","tid":1034834,"uid":34410,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:24:09.000Z","msg":"英國政府真係愈黎愈垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8d9ab6f9482ccd15e9bd2d8d3baf58011311d7","tid":1034834,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:30:24.000Z","msg":"其實邊有勢力去逼佢地立法丫<br />\n又係啲離地idea"}]}